text: Goth Gorshani is a populated place located in Balochistan, on the route between the city of Quetta to Larkana in Sindh in Pakistan. It is located at 28°43'0N 68°15'0E.Location of Goth Gorshani - Falling Rain Genomics The name of the place is derived from a figure of Sufism. ==References== Category:Populated places in Balochistan, Pakistan
title: Goth Gorshani
